Other ARD Representations
While the data frame-based ARD is easy to work with, language-agnostic representations are often useful.


YAML

cards::as_nested_list(ard) |&gt; 
  yaml::as.yaml() |&gt; 
  cat()

variable:
  AGE:
    group1:
      ARM:
        group1_level:
          Placebo:
            stat_name:
              'N':
                stat: 86
                stat_fmt: '86'
                warning: ~
                error: ~
                context: continuous
              mean:
                stat: 75.2093023
